OL,3,CGary Lineker to host new ITV show The
OL,4,CBox after leaving Match of the Day
OL,6,FFormer Match Of The Day host Gary
OL,7,FLineker said he "can't wait" to
OL,8,Fpresent a new ITV game show after his
OL,9,Fexit from the BBC.
OL,11,FThe former footballer, 64, who left
OL,12,Fthe BBC One sports show in May, will
OL,13,Fhost The Box, a new game show which
OL,14,Fwill air on ITV in 2026.
OL,16,FIn the show, 10 yellow boxes house a
OL,17,Fcelebrity contestant who will be
OL,18,Ftransported to unknown locations,
OL,19,Fbefore being released to face whatever
OL,20,Fgame awaits on the other side of the
OL,21,Fdoor.
