OL,3,CGary Lineker to host new ITV show The
OL,4,CBox after leaving Match of the Day
OL,6,FEach week two players will face The
OL,7,FDuel, a finale in which the loser
OL,8,Fleaves the competition for good.
OL,10,FLineker hosted Match of The Day since
OL,11,F1999 until May 2 this year where he
OL,12,Fmade an emotional goodbye.
OL,14,FHis early departure followed a social
OL,15,Fmedia row in which he reshared a post
OL,16,Fabout Zionism featuring a rat, a
OL,17,Fhistorically an anti-semitic symbol.
