OL,3,CGary Lineker to host new ITV show The
OL,4,CBox after leaving Match of the Day
OL,6,FHe made an unreserved apology in a
OL,7,Fvideo on social media and announcing
OL,8,Fhis depature from the BBC where he was
OL,9,Fthe highest-paid presenter.
OL,11,FLineker said: "I can't wait to host
OL,12,FThe Box. I've always felt right at
OL,13,Fhome in the box on a football pitch
OL,14,Fand whilst this is a different
OL,15,Fproposition, the fundamentals are
OL,16,Fsimilar."
OL,18,F"The contestants will have to quickly
OL,19,Fand masterfully work out how each game
OL,20,Fworks, whilst also trying to get ahead
OL,21,Fof the competition to take control."
