OL,6,F"It's going to be unpredictable and
OL,7,Fthrilling to watch, and I'm excited
OL,8,Fthat I get to have a front row seat to
OL,9,Fall the action."
OL,11,FKatie Rawcliffe, director of
OL,12,Fentertainment, reality and daytime
OL,13,Fcommissioning at ITV, said: "Gary is
OL,14,Fthe perfect fit for The Box, an
OL,15,Fentertaining, exhilarating and
OL,16,Fimmersive new format."
