OL,6,FDan Adamson, chief content officer at
OL,7,Fproduction company Twofour, added:
OL,8,F"From the first time we saw those
OL,9,Ficonic yellow boxes open in an
OL,10,Fincredible location we were hooked.
OL,11,FNow, with Gary on board, we have the
OL,12,Fideal master of ceremonies to make
OL,13,Fthis real event telly, he is after all
OL,14,Fa man who knows what it's like under
OL,15,Fpressure in the box.
OL,17,F"He's sure to raise the competitive
OL,18,Fspirit as our cast bursts out of those
OL,19,Fboxes, into unknown, ambitious and
OL,20,Fspectacular challenges."
